  <brief_title>Pregabalin Compared to Gabapentin for Pain Control in Lumbar Disc Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Gabapentin vs. Pregabalin for Post Operative Pain in Lumbar Microdiscectomy: a Randomized Controlled Trial.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
